  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This brightly labeled bottle or waterskin could appear to contain any number of different beverages, from absinthe to wine. However, it's actually a magical trap, and when the bottle is opened, a spider swarm (Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 258) pours out. The swarm stays in the area for 3 rounds, then disappears. Detecting that the bottle is trapped requires a successful DC 25 Perception check made by a character with the trapfinding ability, and disabling it requires a successful DC 25 Disable Device check. After being triggered, the trapped beverage remains a mundane bottle or wineskin.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, summon swarm</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Kobolds Of Golarion",
